description: Jacqueline is a movie actress that is the main star of the "Spy and Sidekick" series. She plays a Pokémon Trainer spy and her partner is Inteleon, the Secret Agent Pokémon. They keep making movie sequels because they`ve all been hit movies. When the filming of her latest movie was interrupted by Team Rocket, who was trying to recruit Inteleon, she instructed her Inteleon to Snipe Shot them and send them flying off the set. Jacqueline`s Inteleon became a role model for Goh`s Sobble.
name: Inteleon (Jacqueline)
